9+08:00</updated><author><name>9airwave</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-06T15:07:09+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573876458"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573876458"&gt;恆指咁耐都唔上26000，今月季結但月中美國議息，市場已反映今年尾減0.5，傳統美股9月10月都係回調，港股來緊下星期似今年最後機會衝26000。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;睇好既：橫行太耐⋯⋯動力指標轉弱，成交縮（3000億好耐無見），暫時（6成）似派貨，升唔穿26000都唔出奇。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;買貨位：我發覺邪邪地，無理由一直都買唔到貨，今次乜都唔寫。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32026080&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=136160221668bc60c8e2d903_58070006"/><published>2025-09-06T15:07:09+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>1e06860986167a0460032dd96a55a338</id><title>突發壞消息，全沽清</title><updated>2025-09-06T15:27:54+08:00</updated><author><name>幸運數字</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-06T15:27:54+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573876640"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573876640"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16479794" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573876640" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250906/20250906_45f546ad86f6888724deDbbNUUyw2Bdm.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/1d6251/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250906/20250906_45f546ad86f6888724deDbbNUUyw2Bdm.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16479794_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a